Package org.aludratest.service.gui.component

Interface Summary
Button Represents a button in a GUI.
Checkbox Represents a checkbox in a GUI.
Dropdownbox Represents a dropdownbox in a GUI.
Element<E extends Element<E>> Parent interface for GUI Elements e.g.
FileField Represents a file field in a GUI.
GenericElement GUI element without a specific assignment to a certain GUI component type.
GUIComponent Parent interface for all Components of a Graphical User Interface, e.g.
GUIComponentFactory Factory for creating components for a GUI service.
InputField Represents an input field in a GUI.
Label Represents a Label in a GUI.
Link Represents a link in a GUI.
RadioButton Represents a radio button on a GUI.
Window Represents a Window/Frame in a GUI.
